	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't know that they are really rare, but around the time that Component Video became more common on devices such as DVD players. Digital TVs like LCDs were coming out and had Component, and cheaper CRT TVs tended to be lucky to have S-Video much less Component. Component was probably more common on more expensive/larger TV sets.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


